msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/spellcasting/spells/bane.md:14
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Casting Time:** 1 action   \n"
"**Range:** 30 feet   \n"
"**Components:** V, S, M (a drop of blood)   \n"
"**Duration:** Concentration, up to 1 minute \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/spellcasting/spells/bane.md:16
msgid ""
"Up to three creatures of your choice that you can see within range must make "
"Charisma saving throws. Whenever a target that fails this saving throw makes "
"an attack roll or a saving throw before the spell ends, the target must roll "
"a d4 and subtract the number rolled from the attack roll or saving throw."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/spellcasting/spells/bane.md:17
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**At Higher Levels.** When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 2nd "
"level or higher, you can target one additional creature for each slot level "
"above 1st. \n"
msgstr ""
